markdownRemark.html: EDIT16, CNCE34403 describes an ideal copy of the Tacuino Opera omnia of 1507 as consisting of eight fascicles dated variously from February 1507 to June 1508. Many surviving copies, however, have other groupings of variously dated fascicles.
